snippet.title: Note Ban: Banks, ATMs Run Out of Cash, Chaos Continues

localized.description:
Note Ban: Banks and ATMs are run out of cash and lead to chaos. Peoples are standing in queues outside ATMs and banks to withdraw cash from their bank accounts. Opposition parties like Congress, TMC, AAP are continuously attacking Modi government in the Parliament over demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
